<ql>
<m1><ql>
<styl>hed,6,48,1<ql>
<m0>Scofflaws flout parking rul<m2><ql>
<ql>
g rul<m0>es in hip, crowded SoBe<ql>
<m1><ue5><m2><ql>
<m4>   LINE 1 IS .94 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS 1.152 INCHES<m2><ql>
